title: Spacious 2 Bedroom in the Heart of Seattle! With 2 Weeks FREE!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 70', 'OR Text', '70', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1112 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Met Tower delivers the best of both worlds – the comforts of your own home while providing all the luxury and convenience of a 5-star hotel.', 'Not enough?', 'You will also enjoy a host of amenities exclusive for residents; private balcony/patio, 24-hour personalized Concierge Service, Indoor Swimming Pool, Spa, Fitness Center and more.', 'Our community is located in the heart of Seattle (98101), we are directly across the street from Amazon so there is no better commute for all you Amazonians!', 'Did we mention that we are in walking distance to some of the most amazing restaurants and retail in all of Seattle, well we are!', 'We also have some of the most convenient transportation within blocks of our community!', 'If that isn’t your style, then our convenient parking garage will be perfect to keep your car at your fingertips to hit the open road.', 'Met Tower goes even further to provide comfort, convenience and luxury for our residents by providing a gorgeous outdoor terrace, dog run, business & entertainment centers and billiards room.', 'You can’t beat the 360 degrees of breathtaking views; from Elliot Bay and the Olympics to the Cascades, each one of our homes offer views that rival any Instagram account and makes you want to have your iPhone on the ready for the next time the sun sets.', 'Features:', 'Above Standard Ceiling Height, City, Water and Queen Anne Views, Wood plank-style flooring, Private Balcony/Patio, Central Air Conditioning, Stainless steel Energy Star® Whirlpool® appliances, Granite countertops, Penthouse Fireplaces, Washer/Dryer, Large Closets, Deluxe kitchens with breakfast bars, 20+ distinct floorplans including private penthouses', 'Community Amenities:', 'State-of-the-art 24-hour fitness center, On-site management and maintenance, Indoor swimming pool and spa, Elevator, Elegant clubhouse with expansive great room, media center, full kitchen and billiards room, Directly across the street from Amazon, Controlled access to building and garage, Access to South Lake Union Trolley right outside, Barolo Restaurant, Sweetgrass Restaurant, Petra Bistro, Vovito & La Caviste all On Site, Underground parking and private garages available, 24 hour concierge service, WI-FI in all common areas, Stunning New Lobby, Zipcars in Parking Garage, Cats and large dogs welcome, private pet area on rooftop, Rooftop deck with bbqs and casual seating', 'Pet Policy', "BFF's Welcomed!", 'Monthly Pet Rent of $50.', 'We have no weight limit restriction.', 'Certain breed restrictions apply.', 'Call today for more details!', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'veW2Pj4E']
